list.abstract: 《AGGRESSIVE》是2008年2月27日发行的一首歌曲，演唱者为BoA，收纳在专辑《THE FACE》中。

yingyinNormal.en: Could be pneumococcal. Most likely an aggressive flu strain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可能是肺炎球菌，很可能是一种急性流感。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, when you get out there. You be aggressive. I know Dad. Not too aggressive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 听着，你去的时候，要有攻击性一点。我知道了，爸。但也别太有攻击性了。

yingyinNormal.en: Or maybe any aggressive predator looks savage to rabbits? Let's go!
yingyinNormal.zh: 或者在兔子眼里，肉食动物有攻击性就算兽性大发？走吧！

yingyinNormal.en: Your machine seems to be even more aggressive than Northern Lights.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的机器看起来比北极光更为激进。

yingyinNormal.en: We train in hand-to-hand combat. It keeps us in shape. And aggressive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们还接受真刀真枪的搏斗训练，这使得我们保持强健，也更好斗。

yingyinNormal.en: I've already developed a virus strain that I think will be more aggressive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我已经研发出一个病种我认为会更有效。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Rise of the Planet of the Apes》

yingyinNormal.en: Maybe I talk too much, or maybe I should have been more, you know, aggressive sexually.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也许我太说得太多了，也许我应该在性方面更主动些。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, but they have no Icee machines. Despite my aggressive letter-writing campaign, I might add.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没错，可是那里没有刨冰机，还完全不理睬我那么多封投诉信，错上加错。

yingyinNormal.en: Step 3: Turn the lifeboat sideways to the waves, accompanied by harsh, aggressive use of the whistle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 步骤三：之后让船侧冲着浪头，并尖锐有力地吹着口哨。

yingyinNormal.en: And then we have the fer-de-lance, and this one is more aggressive because he always like to bite you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这里还有矛头蛇，这种蛇更具攻击性，因为它们喜欢咬人。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《大卫·贝克汉姆：探索未知之境》

yingyinNormal.en: I didn't know how it was gonna turn out, But I was like, "I'm just gonna be really, really aggressive."
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不知道结果会怎样，但是我将非常非常具有攻击性

yingyinNormal.en: Yes. What I mean is thousands of years ago, predators survived through their aggressive hunting instincts.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可以，我是说几千年以前食肉动物捕猎的本能一直存在着。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I thought there might be some aggressive questions that, made me nervous, and so I wrote down my remarks.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我料到可能会碰到一些质问会让我紧张，所以我就把评论写下来了。

yingyinNormal.en: But if you believe that A.I. can transcend its creators' original mission, and you introduced the theory of fuzzy driving in order to make the car more aggressive, more human-like, then why couldn't the computer override your safety controls?
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是如果你认为人工智能会超越创造者的初始任务并且你引入了模糊智能驾驶以使得车辆更加自主，更像人类，那为什么计算机不会重写安全控制模块呢？
